&lt;h2 id="-firewall"&gt;ğŸ”¥ Firewall
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Firewall&lt;/strong&gt; is a network security device that monitors and filters incoming/outgoing traffic based on organization&amp;rsquo;s security policies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ğŸ”¹ Prevents unauthorized access to internal systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ğŸ”¹ Supports data traffic control rules.&lt;/p&gt;
