&lt;h2 id="-nginx"&gt;ğŸŒ Nginx
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nginx&lt;/strong&gt; is an open-source web server, widely used for its ability to handle many concurrent connections with high performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ğŸ”¹ Supports web server, reverse proxy, load balancing, caching.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ğŸ”¹ Suitable for microservices systems and containers.&lt;/p&gt;
